 # ActiveAndroidRx
 
+Fork from vicpinm repository.
+
 Wrapper around ActiveAndroid which introduces reactive queries with SQLBrite from Square (https://github.com/square/sqlbrite).
 You can use it as alternative for Android loaders! 
 
